  <thing id="cuUWPain2" name="Sadistic Strike" description="Within one combat per day, whenever you confirm a critical with a melee attack, you experience a surge of pleasure, granting you a +5 ft. profane bonus to your land speed, a +1 profane bonus to your attack rolls, and a –1 penalty to your AC. Multiple instances of confirming a critical in the combat stack. For example, if you confirm a critical three times in one combat, you gain a +15 ft. profane bonus to your land speed, a +3 profane bonus to attack rolls and a –3 penalty to your AC. The bonuses last until the end of the encounter." compset="ClSpecial">
