  <thing id="cuUWSloth2" name="Idleness" description="You are so lazy, not even magic can make you do anything you do not want to do. You gain a +4 morale bonus to all saves against enchantment spells and effects, and whenever you are the target of such a spell, you may rebound the spell back to its caster. To reflect the spell, you must succeed at a Will save against the spell&apos;s DC, including your +4 morale bonus. If you succeed, you affect the caster as if you had cast the spell yourself. At 10th level, you may rebound the spell to any opponent within 20 ft. of the original caster." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Gain +4 morale bonus vs. enchantment spells and effects and can rebound effect on caster">
